  <!-- Decay settings -->
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayRate>Decay Rate (% per interval):</RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayRate>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayRateDesc>Fraction of current karma lost each decay tick. Higher = faster decay toward minimum.</RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayRateDesc>

  <RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayInterval>Decay Interval (minutes):</RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayInterval>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayIntervalDesc>How often the automatic karma decay tick runs (prevents permanent max karma).</RICS.Economy.KarmaDecayIntervalDesc>

  <RICS.Economy.KarmaMinDecay>Minimum Decay Amount:</RICS.Economy.KarmaMinDecay>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaMinDecayDesc>Absolute floor of karma lost per decay tick (even at very low karma).</RICS.Economy.KarmaMinDecayDesc>

  <!-- Store &amp; Event karma impact -->
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaPerStoreItem>Karma per Store Item:</RICS.Economy.KarmaPerStoreItem>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaPerStoreItemDesc>Karma gained when a viewer buys something from the store (reduced to limit abuse).</RICS.Economy.KarmaPerStoreItemDesc>

  <RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerBadEvent>Karma Loss per Bad Event:</RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerBadEvent>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerBadEventDesc>Stronger karma penalty when a bad event is triggered by chat.</RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerBadEventDesc>

  <RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerGoodEvent>Karma Gain per Good Event:</RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerGoodEvent>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerGoodEventDesc>Karma awarded when a good/neutral event is triggered.</RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerGoodEventDesc>

  <RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerNeutralEvent>Karma Gain per Neutral Event:</RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerNeutralEvent>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerNeutralEventDesc>Small karma gain for neutral events.</RICS.Economy.KarmaGainPerNeutralEventDesc>

  <RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerDoomEvent>Karma Loss per Doom Event:</RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerDoomEvent>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerDoomEventDesc>Heavy karma penalty for doom-level events.</RICS.Economy.KarmaLossPerDoomEventDesc>

  <!-- Reward multipliers -->
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMin>Minimum Karma Multiplier:</RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMin>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMinDesc>Coin reward multiplier when karma is at its lowest (e.g. 0.30 = 30% of base reward).</RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMinDesc>

  <RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMax>Maximum Karma Multiplier:</RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMax>
  <RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMaxDesc>Coin reward multiplier when karma is at its highest (e.g. 2.00 = 200% of base reward).</RICS.Economy.KarmaMultiplierMaxDesc>
